The user enters a username and password into the username and password textfields respectively and presses the Sign In button. The system validates the username and password combination by querying the system database. The system database does not find a match with the username and password combination. The system displays and error message and returns the user to the Partner Login page. Forgotten Password Course The system displays the Partner Login page. The user clicks on the Forgot my password link. The system prompts the user for their account email address. The user enters their account email address and clicks the Reset Password button. The system queries the database for the account email address. If a match is found a Reset Password Confirmation email is sent to the email address.
